data.title: 7-9 SeriesBooks 2024
data.meta_description: 7-9_SeriesBooks_2024 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document discusses series books that students can read as part of a reading challenge. It states that a student can read up to three books from an approved series as their official reading. Students may also read up to five additional books from a series for personal enjoyment that do not count towards their official reading. The document encourages students to continue reading more books from a series they enjoyed after completing the challenge.
